11#include "rtc_base/copy_on_write_buffer.h"
12
13#include <stddef.h>
14
15namespace rtc {
16
17CopyOnWriteBuffer::CopyOnWriteBuffer() : offset_(0), size_(0) {
18 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
19}
20
21CopyOnWriteBuffer::CopyOnWriteBuffer(const CopyOnWriteBuffer& buf)
22 : buffer_(buf.buffer_), offset_(buf.offset_), size_(buf.size_) {}
23
24CopyOnWriteBuffer::CopyOnWriteBuffer(CopyOnWriteBuffer&& buf)
25 : buffer_(std::move(buf.buffer_)), offset_(buf.offset_), size_(buf.size_) {
26 buf.offset_ = 0;
27 buf.size_ = 0;
28 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
29}
30
31CopyOnWriteBuffer::CopyOnWriteBuffer(const std::string& s)
32 : CopyOnWriteBuffer(s.data(), s.length()) {}
33
34CopyOnWriteBuffer::CopyOnWriteBuffer(size_t size)
35 : buffer_(size > 0 ? new RefCountedBuffer(size) : nullptr),
36 offset_(0),
37 size_(size) {
38 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
39}
40
41CopyOnWriteBuffer::CopyOnWriteBuffer(size_t size, size_t capacity)
42 : buffer_(size > 0 || capacity > 0 ? new RefCountedBuffer(size, capacity)
43 : nullptr),
44 offset_(0),
45 size_(size) {
46 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
47}
48
49CopyOnWriteBuffer::~CopyOnWriteBuffer() = default;
50
51bool CopyOnWriteBuffer::operator==(const CopyOnWriteBuffer& buf) const {
52 // Must either be the same view of the same buffer or have the same contents.
53 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
54 RTC_DCHECK(buf.IsConsistent());
55 return size_ == buf.size_ &&
56 (cdata() == buf.cdata() || memcmp(cdata(), buf.cdata(), size_) == 0);
57}
58
59void CopyOnWriteBuffer::SetSize(size_t size) {
60 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
61 if (!buffer_) {
62 if (size > 0) {
63 buffer_ = new RefCountedBuffer(size);
64 offset_ = 0;
65 size_ = size;
66 }
67 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
68 return;
69 }
70
71 if (size <= size_) {
72 size_ = size;
73 return;
74 }
75
76 UnshareAndEnsureCapacity(std::max(capacity(), size));
77 buffer_->SetSize(size + offset_);
78 size_ = size;
79 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
80}
81
82void CopyOnWriteBuffer::EnsureCapacity(size_t new_capacity) {
83 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
84 if (!buffer_) {
85 if (new_capacity > 0) {
86 buffer_ = new RefCountedBuffer(0, new_capacity);
87 offset_ = 0;
88 size_ = 0;
89 }
90 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
91 return;
92 } else if (new_capacity <= capacity()) {
93 return;
94 }
95
96 UnshareAndEnsureCapacity(new_capacity);
97 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
98}
99
100void CopyOnWriteBuffer::Clear() {
101 if (!buffer_)
102 return;
103
104 if (buffer_->HasOneRef()) {
105 buffer_->Clear();
106 } else {
107 buffer_ = new RefCountedBuffer(0, capacity());
108 }
109 offset_ = 0;
110 size_ = 0;
111 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
112}
113
114void CopyOnWriteBuffer::UnshareAndEnsureCapacity(size_t new_capacity) {
115 if (buffer_->HasOneRef() && new_capacity <= capacity()) {
116 return;
117 }
118
119 buffer_ =
120 new RefCountedBuffer(buffer_->data() + offset_, size_, new_capacity);
121 offset_ = 0;
122 RTC_DCHECK(IsConsistent());
123}
124
125} // namespace rtc
